trans:
Welcome back, Yasemin.
I see a similar shape in a few different parts in your coffee grounds. When I look at it carefully and as far as I understand from its energy, it is a sardonyx stone, Yasemin. I think this symbol of good fortune is the best proof that all the misfortunes and troubles you have encountered so far have come to an end. You will finally meet an opportunity that will change your misfortune. But what's interesting here is that this opportunity will be offered by someone you don't really like. Even if you don't want to consider it at first, your logic will outweigh and you will take the most important step for your career and even your future.
Let's continue with the details in your cup whispers, Yasemin;
On the lip part of your cup, Yasemin, I see your boyfriend with an ace card in his hand which is the most powerful card in the deck of cards and he is holding it out towards you, right in front of him. This image indicates that he is going to make a move about your recently ended relationship. As you know, the ace also symbolizes the number 1. I can say that this indicates that he is going to make this move in November. I would say let's wait and see what kind of days await you, but I think exciting days await you.
I see a bee on the top left of your cup, Yasemin. ğŸ Bees are hardworking animals. The fact that it appears in your horoscope indicates that you will make an important investment in your future. This investment may require you to work hard and even devote the time remaining from your education life and lessons to this investment.
